track_notes:
Classif E.
Long path from Sambuco to surround from North the steep western rocky side of Mt Nebius. 
The southern approach would be equally far but warmer for solar exposition. 
You find a first Point at East with cross but the true summit is at West with a dizzy view on the valley 1500 meter down.
Reward of exhausting trek is tasting the SAMBUCANO LAMB in the Sambuco Hostel.
track_title: 3 summit trail  Mt NEBIUS long but easy.  Sambucos LAMB x dinner.
